---
import cv from "../../../cv.json";
import HeroImage from "./HeroImage.astro";
const { name } = cv.basic;
---

<section
  class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center max-w-7xl mx-auto"
  aria-labelledby="hero-title"
>
  <div
    class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center w-full"
  >
    <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8 order-2 lg:order-1 text-left">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h1
          id="hero-title"
          class="reveal text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter text-(--text-primary) leading-[1.1] md:leading-[0.95]"
          style="--delay: 200ms"
        >
          Software hecho <br />
          <span class="text-blue-600">a la medida.</span>
        </h1>

        <p
          class="reveal max-w-xl text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-(--text-secondary) leading-relaxed"
          style="--delay: 300ms"
        >
        Construyo herramientas digitales que simplifican el día a día de tu negocio. Desarrollo sistemas web y aplicaciones enfocadas en <strong class="text-(--text-primary) font-semibold"
            >ordenar tus procesos</strong
          > y ahorrarte tiempo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-4 reveal"
        style="--delay: 400ms"
      >
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/tu-numero"
          class="no-underline px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:bg-blue-700 transition-all text-center shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/10"
          aria-label="Contactar por WhatsApp"
        >
          Hablar por WhatsApp
        </a>
        <a
          href="#proyectos"
          class="no-underline px-8 py-4 border-2 border-(--text-primary) text-(--text-primary) text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:bg-(--text-primary) hover:text-white transition-all text-center"
        >
          Casos de Estudio
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-5 order-1 lg:order-2">
        <HeroImage name={name} src="/portafolio/images/me.jpeg" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
